cs.LG, cs.DB, cs.IR, cs.SI, cs.CE

The paper introduces a web platform for time-series data analysis, which involves machine learning and database technologies. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.DB (Databases), as the platform involves data storage and retrieval. The paper also mentions the use of algorithms for time-series analysis, which could fall under cs.IR (Information Retrieval) or cs.SI (Social and Information Networks). Finally, the paper discusses the interdisciplinary nature of the platform, which could be relevant to cs.CE (Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science).
